features: SYMMETRICAL SHAPE: No “right side up” silicone pacifier for babies are fuss-free and won’t need to be adjusted to sit properly in baby’s mouth and fits perfectly under nose for easy breathing.
SILICONE NIPPLE: The BPA-free silicone boy and girl pacifier has the signature MAM design, with silky SkinSoft material and a symmetrical shape that's ideal for jaw and teeth development.
SELF - STERILIZING CASE: Add water and pop into the microwave to sterilize MAM silicone pacifiers 0-6 months in just 3 minutes and store in case for at home and travel to protect the pacifiers.
VENTILATED & COMFORTABLE SHIELD: These cute pacifiers for babies have a curved sterilizing shield with openings to keep baby comfortable, prevent moisture build-up, and allow baby’s skin to breathe.

HIGH QUALITY: Approved by 94% of babies*, our 100% BPA & BPS free silicone pacifiers meet or exceed US safety standards and are extremely durable while being soft and flexible for your baby's comfort.
body.description: The MAM Original Matte Pacifier was developed by leading pediatric dentists and developmental psychologists to provide maximum comfort and style for babies 0-6 months of age.* MAM pacifiers for baby feature an innovative nipple designed to promote healthy oral development and with the help of a built-in air channel, the pacifier naturally flattens and extends when sucked, mimicking a human nipple during breastfeeding. All MAM pacifiers are orthodontic, featuring a symmetrical nipple that fits perfectly in baby's mouth at any angle and life-like, SkinSoft textured silicone that feels more natural, just like mom. With multiple pacifier shapes and shield sizes to pick from, MAM nipples are easily accepted by babies of all ages, with 94% nipple acceptance among babies tested.** Our Original plain pacifier comes in a variety of neutral matte colors to coordinate with your babies' everyday outfits! Pacifiers kept in the closed box will remain clean for up to 48 hours: Fill pacifier case with water. Place pacifier in the self-sterilizing case with the nipple facing down. Follow package instructions for microwave setting. Cool completely before use. *Developed with the International Children's Medical Research Society. **Market research 2010-2020, tested with 1,572 babies

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Mam pacifiers saved me with my third baby! This is the only pacifier they will take. These are easy to clean, baby can hold them easily, and works especially well for breastfeeding mothers as I feel it didn't cause any nipple confusion.Down side, moisture gets in the nipple really easy so you can't submerge them in water. I boil them when I first get them for 5 minutes, use tongs to squeeze the nipple to fill with the boiling water then use tongs again to squeeze the water out. After that I wash them with soap and water and put them in the sterilizer.I typically get new ones every month because they get lost.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: All 3 of my kids took mam pacifiers and all breastfed. Much lighter than other pacis. I honestly don’t know what I would do without this pacifier. Just be sure to buy new ones after a while the nipple will wear out and saliva will get into it. Great price and quality.

reviews.reviewText: My baby loves these. And they stay put in his mouth better then most other pacifiers. Nice and light weight. The problem is water gets into the nipple and doesn’t dry completely.
